N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 256.20 - Supplementary inspection-all holders

State Regulations

At least once a year an inspection shall be made of all
holders by competent independent inspectors or engineers not in the employ of
the company. The inspectors or engineers shall submit complete reports to the
responsible operating official. Notes
